main event: Witnessed an unidentified flying object in Columbus, Ohio on September 6, 1967.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 20 minutes by multiple witnesses., The object was seen through binoculars and appeared similar to the bottom of a spaceship with cracks in its surface., Witnesses reported the object's pulsating light reminiscent of a lightning bug., Observers included a man walking his dog and a father and son with telescopes., The Air Force followed up with Mr. [REDACTED] to complete further observation forms.
sighted object: an unidentified flying object described as having a pulsating light
witness description: Various local residents including Mr. [REDACTED] and his neighbors
